Event.name: Cycle_of_life_and_death
Event.definition: <def-root>A <fen>Protagonist</fen> is born or sprouts, lives, dies, and then is dead.</def-root>

Arg.name: Protagonist
Arg.definition: <def-root><fen>Protagonist</fen> identifies the being or entity that is dead or alive. <ex><fex name="Prot">Frank</fex> was <t>dead</t>.</ex> </def-root>
